---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
import Header from '../components/Header';
import Footer from '../components/Footer.astro';
---

<Layout title="Privacy Policy | Sloan Property Progressions" description="Privacy policy for Sloan Property Progressions.">
  <Header client:load />
  <main class="bg-white pt-28 pb-20">
    <div class="container mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 max-w-3xl">
      <h1 class="text-4xl font-[Rajdhani] font-bold text-[#334D2B] mb-2">Privacy Policy</h1>
      <p class="text-gray-500 text-sm mb-10">Last updated: May 2026</p>
      <div class="space-y-8 text-gray-700 leading-relaxed">
        <section><h2 class="text-xl font-[Rajdhani] font-bold text-[#334D2B] mb-3">Who We Are</h2><p>Sloan Property Progressions operates this website for land clearing, forestry mulching, trail clearing, fence-line clearing, and acreage cleanup inquiries across Northeast Texas.</p></section>
        <section><h2 class="text-xl font-[Rajdhani] font-bold text-[#334D2B] mb-3">Information We Collect</h2><p>When you request a quote, we may collect your name, email, phone number, property address, photos, project details, and any notes you choose to provide.</p></section>
        <section><h2 class="text-xl font-[Rajdhani] font-bold text-[#334D2B] mb-3">How We Use It</h2><p>We use submitted information to respond to inquiries, scope projects, schedule estimates, improve the website, and communicate about requested services. We do not sell personal information.</p></section>
        <section><h2 class="text-xl font-[Rajdhani] font-bold text-[#334D2B] mb-3">Third-Party Tools</h2><p>This website may use hosting, analytics, CRM, form, or scheduling providers. Those providers may process information according to their own policies.</p></section>
        <section><h2 class="text-xl font-[Rajdhani] font-bold text-[#334D2B] mb-3">Contact</h2><p>Questions? Email <a href="mailto:quotes@sloanpropertyprogressions.com" class="text-[#F37121] hover:underline">quotes@sloanpropertyprogressions.com</a>.</p></section>
      </div>
    </div>
  </main>
  <Footer />
</Layout>
